"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-09-olympics-diver-gets-massive-penalty-getting-cold-feet-last-minute-21391997\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Moritz Wesemann's hopes of winning a medal in the final of theOlympic3m springboard finalwere effectively ended after he got cold feet.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Moritz Wesemann's hopes\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 23}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 35, \"to\": 42}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 46, \"to\": 55}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympic3m\", \"from\": 59, \"to\": 71}, {\"ngram\": \"springboard finalwere\", \"from\": 72, \"to\": 93}, {\"ngram\": \"cold feet\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheGermanneeded a flawless dive at the start of round five in order to haul himself back into contention of a podium finish.\", \"from\": 137, \"to\": 261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"TheGermanneeded\", \"from\": 137, \"to\": 152}, {\"ngram\": \"a flawless dive\", \"from\": 153, \"to\": 168}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 181}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 204}, {\"ngram\": \"contention\", \"from\": 231, \"to\": 241}, {\"ngram\": \"a podium finish\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wesemann had opted to attempt a dive incorporating four-and-a-half somersaults, which represented a difficulty rating of 3.8.\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 388, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wesemann\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 271}, {\"ngram\": \"a dive\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 299}, {\"ngram\": \"four-and-a-half somersaults\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 341}, {\"ngram\": \"a difficulty rating\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 380}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, as he prepared for takeoff, the reigning European champion mistimed his approach and retreated to the safety of the start of the board.\", \"from\": 390, \"to\": 540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999652503282662, \"rank\": 3.380160524003741e-05, \"text\": \"European champion\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"takeoff\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 431}, {\"ngram\": \"his approach\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 485}, {\"ngram\": \"the safety\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 526}, {\"ngram\": \"the board\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'That's known as a balk, which is formally known as a re-start,' explained BBC diving commentator Leon Taylor.\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 617, \"end\": 620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9875198850919097, \"rank\": 0.012602591509732168, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 640, \"end\": 651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Taylor\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Leon Taylor\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Taylor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leon_Taylor\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a balk\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Wesemann was coming in on his hurdle step and had no chance of making the dive and decided to stop.'\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 755, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wesemann\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 663}, {\"ngram\": \"his hurdle step\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 696}, {\"ngram\": \"no chance\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 714}, {\"ngram\": \"the dive\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To his credit, the 22-year-old quickly regained his composure and completed his dive, albeit in the knowledge he would be penalised for his moment of hesitancy 'He would have been getting sevens if it wasn't for the re-start,' added Taylor, upon confirmation of the two-point punishment Wesemann received from each of the seven judges.\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his credit\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"his composure\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 818}, {\"ngram\": \"his dive\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"the knowledge\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"his moment\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 903}, {\"ngram\": \"hesitancy\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"Taylor\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 996}, {\"ngram\": \"confirmation\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"the two-point punishment Wesemann\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1052}, {\"ngram\": \"the seven judges\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1091}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But of course what happens sometimes you have to stop for safety reasons and make the dive.'\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"safety reasons\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"the dive\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Great Britain's Jack Laugher, meanwhile,described a poor third dive as the 'nail in the coffin moment' for his Olympic hopes after finishing seventh.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1339, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1206, \"end\": 1210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"score\": 0.844794934846344, \"rank\": 0.1828982099471313, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a poor third dive\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1257}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'nail\", \"f