"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1609}, {\"ngram\": \"an inward three-and-a-half somersault\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1671}, {\"ngram\": \"his medal chances\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on that moment he said: 'It was the nail in the coffin moment at that point really.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1846, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"the nail\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1803}, {\"ngram\": \"the coffin moment\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1824}, {\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I gave it my everything and really put my all on the line, unfortunately it just did not go well.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my everything\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1872}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I wish at that point I could've pulled out, but I am really happy that I continued on because I am a fantastic athlete and I always see things through, it just wasn't the fairy-tale I wanted it to be.'\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 2150, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1969}, {\"ngram\": \"a fantastic athlete\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2067}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"the fairy-tale\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China's Xie Siyi won the gold medal, while teammate Wang Zongyuan finished with silver and Mexico's Osmar Olvera Ibarra claimed bronze.\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2152, \"end\": 2157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6905495260057731, \"rank\": 0.3991302245052955, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.o